00:10:48.342 --> 00:10:53.316
1 or 3 into the hat.
Player II then chooses,

00:10:53.316 --> 00:10:57.794
although really Player II only
has choices to make if there's

00:10:57.794 --> 00:11:02.211
some money in the hat,
and Player II has two choices

00:11:02.211 --> 00:11:05.730
in this particular game in
either case.

00:11:05.730 --> 00:11:11.283
Either Player II is going to
add $1 or $3 into the hat or

00:11:11.283 --> 00:11:17.431
