money so she makes a net profit

00:11:39.926 --> 00:11:43.440
of 1.
If the money is taken out by

00:11:43.440 --> 00:11:48.666
Player II then she loses 1.
Down here if II matches her

00:11:48.666 --> 00:11:54.397
