01:03:18.119 --> 01:03:22.942
These branches in the tree,
the branches,

01:03:22.942 --> 01:03:28.610
here they are,
the branches are called edges.

01:03:28.610 --> 01:03:33.355
So a tree consists of nodes,
edges, and these missing dots

01:03:33.355 --> 01:03:37.233
are the end nodes.
The end nodes are associated

01:03:37.233 --> 01:03:38.739
with payoffs.
