01:03:44.032 --> 01:03:49.900
somebody whose turn it is to
make a decision at that node.

01:03:49.900 --> 01:03:54.681
These other nodes,
the ones that aren't end nodes

01:03:54.681 --> 01:03:58.895
are called decision nodes.
